data.value:
ANNdotNET - deep learning tool on .NET platform.
ANNdotNET uses the folowing third party open source libraries:
- CNTK - Microsoft Congnitive Toolkit, with MIT License, - Fluent.ibbon - WPF Ribbon control like in Office , with MIT License - ZedGraph - charting control, with lgpl2.1 license, - ClosedXML - reading and writing Excel files, with MIT license, - Excel-DNA - Excel add-ins using .NET, with MIT license
